.TH WLA\-6800 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-6800 \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the Motorola 6800
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-6800
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-6800
assembles Motorola 6800 source code to a WLA DX object file.
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wla\-6801 (1),
.BR wla\-6809 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
